{"tid":1353170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公務員參與罷工的權利 (公務員事務局 2006年3月)","createTime":"2019-07-23T02:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T23:52:35.000Z","uid":229801,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9afc582f7c92d1542f4d2bcf474ac5ea9ebe52e4","tid":1353170,"uid":229801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"2005年8月1日港九拯溺員工會發動罷工，約有270名康樂及文化事務署拯溺員未經許可缺勤，抗議康文署外判大角嘴體育館救生服務。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>立法會 CB(1)1067/05-06(05)號討論文件</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結論</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府充分尊重<ins>公務員所享有的權利</ins>，包括組織和參加工<br />\n會、<ins>罷工的權利與自由</ins>。在員工因 參與罷工行動而缺勤的情況<br />\n下，當 局 是 基 於<ins> &ldquo; 無 工 無 酬 &rdquo; </ins>的 原 則 扣 除 有 關 人 員 在 缺 勤 期 間 的<br />\n薪金的。該項措施並無侵犯公務員的罷工權利。</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Ffiles%2Fpanel060314c.pdf&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUisg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=3215e24c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"4c8b732d3e0ebefe963702cbbcc9be0a9ffc8dd0","tid":1353170,"uid":229801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9afc582f7c92d1542f4d2bcf474ac5ea9ebe52e4","tid":1353170,"uid":229801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:12:37.000Z","msg":"2005年8月1日港九拯溺員工會發動罷工，約有270名康樂及文化事務署拯溺員未經許可缺勤，抗議康文署外判大角嘴體育館救生服務。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>立法會 CB(1)1067/05-06(05)號討論文件</ins></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">結論</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">政府充分尊重<ins>公務員所享有的權利</ins>，包括組織和參加工<br />\n會、<ins>罷工的權利與自由</ins>。在員工因 參與罷工行動而缺勤的情況<br />\n下，當 局 是 基 於<ins> &ldquo; 無 工 無 酬 &rdquo; </ins>的 原 則 扣 除 有 關 人 員 在 缺 勤 期 間 的<br />\n薪金的。該項措施並無侵犯公務員的罷工權利。</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.csb.gov.hk%2Ftc_chi%2Finfo%2Ffiles%2Fpanel060314c.pdf&d=3INNoT16QYf2eZrqTwRUisg1Od0Dt6CGL4wHSLmh2%2Bg%3D&h=3215e24c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.csb.gov.hk/tc_chi/info/files/panel060314c.pdf</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"3d6379c089480f68c71ed2002999e10f649fc2b3","tid":1353170,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:20:32.000Z","msg":"我係一個揸單程證落黎嘅大陸女人...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1353162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1353162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fa7c4196ffeaf7e82749b0cbd78c42622223a1fc","tid":1353170,"uid":170185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"5556afec52ff5dc18e637feb1e59c9b6bb4270e4","tid":1353170,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:32:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7bf1348a7b57bd997310ba947c7e492048a722","tid":1353170,"uid":259820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:43:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07bbd25e6cfd44ddf32ef96291697866809a58c7","tid":1353170,"uid":156298,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T00:44:55.000Z","msg":"唔好推啲後生公務員出來，一見光就冇得升。到時有位就藍絲上晒。"},{"pid":"a72b682ddce544ed2f2b4bd0859a09fc4c90b2f9","tid":1353170,"uid":271199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:02:16.000Z","msg":"726 伊利沙白醫院網球場 5.30pm至7pm<br />\n726 機場見 1pm至12am<br />\n727 元朗捉精靈 全日"},{"pid":"f2581f339e98e2e8f31f95d2ff5ac75ef83070c5","tid":1353170,"uid":95221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal